title: 256B.0631 PROHIBITION ON COST-SHARING.
text:
MS 2023 Supp [Repealed, 2023 c 70 art 16 s 23]
Effective January 1, 2024, the medical assistance benefit plan must not include cost-sharing or deductibles for any medical assistance recipient or benefit.
MS 2022 [Repealed, 2023 c 70 art 16 s 23]
MS 2023 Supp [Repealed, 2023 c 70 art 16 s 23]
